Data collection procedures
As Popper et al. (2009) used a military sample, we will sample participants with military experience. We are aware of the DoD requirement to have DoD review by
the Human Research Protection Officer (HRPO) and we will obtain this HRPO review prior to implementing any aspects of this study.
Participants will be recruited using Prolific online data collection platform. Individuals meeting the study criteria will be able to see our HIT research
announcement (abbreviated summary of the study -- see attachment to this application) at which point they may opt to participate in the study. Once potential
